These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 9

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-9-1::.
There 4 different types of food: carrot, cauliflower, lime, pumpkin
4 different games are played: go, mah-jongg, bridge, canasta
House: modern, townhouse, tower, farmhouse
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, bus, scooter, van
 1. the townhouse house is somewhere to the right of the person driving the van##5
 2. the person eating pumpkin is not to the right of the person driving the bus##8
 3. the person playing go is somewhere to the right of the person playing mah-jongg##5
 4. the person eating carrot is somewhere to the left of the modern house##5
 5. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person driving the van##1
 6. the person playing canasta and the farmhouse house have different parity positions##9
 7. the person playing mah-jongg is not to the left of the person playing mah-jongg##8
 8. the person eating cauliflower is not to the left of the modern house##8
 9. the townhouse house is somewhere to the right of the person playing bridge##5
10. the farmhouse house is somewhere between the person driving the boat and the townhouse house##7
11. the person eating cauliflower is somewhere to the left of the person eating lime##5
12. the modern house is not the person playing go##6
13. the person driving the scooter is not to the right of the farmhouse house##8
14. the person playing go is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
15. the tower house and the person playing canasta have different parity positions##9
16. the person eating cauliflower is not the tower house##6
17. the person eating pumpkin is somewhere to the left of the person playing canasta##5
18. the person playing go and the modern house have different parity positions##9
19. the person eating cauliflower is somewhere to the left of the person driving the van##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |    3    |    4     |
| Food          | carrot  | cauliflower | pumpkin | lime     |
| Music-Genre   | bridge    | mah-jongg        | go | canasta   |
| Nationality   | tower | modern   | farmhouse   | townhouse |
| Transport     | boat    | scooter     | van     | bus      |

