.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-9-2::.
House: futuristic, modern, art-deco, craftsman
City: hamburg, colone, berlin, nizza
4 different pets are kept: bird, guinea-pig, horse, mouse
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, jet-ski, motorbike, skateboard
 1. the craftsman house and the owner of the guinea-pig have the same parity positions##9
 2. the person driving the motorbike is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
 3. the art-deco house is not the person driving the skateboard##6
 4. the owner of the guinea-pig is in an odd position##4
 5. the person traveling to colone is not to the right of the art-deco house##8
 6. the owner of the mouse is not to the right of the modern house##8
 7. the person traveling to berlin is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the craftsman house is somewhere to the right of the modern house##5
 9. the person driving the boat is the owner of the horse##1
10. the person driving the boat is on the far right##1
11. the person traveling to colone is not to the right of the person driving the jet-ski##8
12. the person traveling to hamburg is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to berlin##5
13. the person driving the skateboard is not to the left of the art-deco house##8
14. the person driving the skateboard and the person traveling to hamburg have the same parity positions##9
15. the owner of the mouse is between the person driving the jet-ski and the craftsman house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |     3      |     4     |
| Food          | art-deco    | modern  | craftsman | futuristic |
| Movie-Genre   | colone | hamburg   | nizza     | berlin    |
| Pet           | bird    | mouse      | guinea-pig | horse     |
| Transport     | jet-ski | skateboard | motorbike  | boat      |

