 5. the person eating eggplant and the japanese have different parity positions##9
 6. the person who's sport is weightlifting is not to the right of the chinese##8
 7. the cottage house is not to the left of the japanese##8
 8. the person who's sport is climbing is somewhere to the left of the craftsman house##5
 9. the japanese is between the person who's sport is weightlifting and the gothic-revival house##2
10. the gothic-revival house is between the japanese and the person eating raspberry##2
11. the japanese is on the left or right of the gothic-revival house##3
12. the cottage house is not to the left of the japanese##8
13. the person eating mango is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
14. the cottage house is not to the left of the cottage house##8
15. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left of the cottage house##1
16. the russian is not to the left of the gothic-revival house##8

