City: boston, paris, new-york, venice
 1. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1
 2. the person watching comedy movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching crime movies##5
 3. the person drinking fanta and the victorian house have different parity positions##9
 4. the futuristic house is on the left or right of the person traveling to new-york##3
 5. the futuristic house is not the person watching comedy movies##6
 6. the craftsman house and the person watching crime movies have the same parity positions##9
 7. the craftsman house is somewhere between the person traveling to venice and the person drinking lemonade##7
 8. the victorian house is not to the left of the person watching superhero movies##8
 9. the person drinking almond-milk is not the person watching crime movies##6
10. the person drinking iced-tea is not to the right of the palace house##8
11. the person traveling to paris is not the person drinking lemonade##6
12. the craftsman house and the person watching crime movies have the same parity positions##9
13. the craftsman house is the person drinking fanta##1
14. the palace house is somewhere to the right of the victorian house##5
15. the person traveling to boston is not to the left of the person drinking almond-milk##8
16. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the craftsman house##1
17. the person watching superhero movies is not the person traveling to boston##6
18. the person traveling to new-york is somewhere to the left of the person drinking fanta##5

.:: Answer ::.
