10. the pilot is somewhere to the right of the person who growsdahlia##5
11. the tiparillo-smoker is the person who growspoppy##1
12. the vegafina-smoker is not to the left of the owner of the fish##8
13. the owner of the fish is on the left of the pall-mall-smoker##1
14. the owner of the hamster is somewhere between the owner of the mouse and the person who growsaconite##7

