 3. the engineer is not to the right of the person eating carrot##8
 4. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the right of the person drinking milk##5
 5. the person playing canasta and the person eating grapefruit have the same parity positions##9
 6. the manager is somewhere between the person playing canasta and the person eating carrot##7
 7. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the scientist##1
 8. the person drinking milk is somewhere to the right of the person drinking soy-milk##5
 9. the manager is not to the right of the person eating cauliflower##8
10. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person playing whist##3
11. the manager is somewhere to the left of the person drinking coffee##5
12. the bartender is somewhere to the right of the person drinking fanta##5
13. the bartender is on the far left or far right##3
14. the person playing go is not the person drinking soy-milk##6
15. the person eating lemon is on the left of the person eating carrot##1
16. the person eating cauliflower is somewhere to the right of the person eating carrot##5
17. the person playing canasta is somewhere to the left of the person drinking coffee##5

.:: Answer ::.
