 5. the person driving the helicopter is somewhere to the right of the person eating radish##5
 6. the nigerian is not the person driving the trike##6
 7. the doctor is not to the right of the indonesian##8
 8. the entrepreneur is somewhere to the left of the person driving the roller##5
 9. the coach and the french have different parity positions##9
10. the person eating avocado and the french have different parity positions##9
11. the teacher is not the person driving the trike##6
12. the nigerian is not to the left of the person driving the helicopter##8
13. the person eating radish is not to the left of the person eating lemon##8
14. the japanese is on the left or right of the person eating cucumber##3
15. the person eating cucumber is not to the left of the nigerian##8
16. the indonesian is not to the right of the person eating lemon##8
