.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-9-16::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, mirinda, sprite, tea
There 4 different types of food: carrot, cherry, kiwi, mango
City: london, miami, nizza, marseilles
House: tower, gothic-revival, craftsman, victorian
 1. the person drinking mirinda is in an odd position##4
 2. the person traveling to marseilles and the gothic-revival house have different parity positions##9
 3. the victorian house is on the left or right of the person eating mango##3
 4. the person eating carrot is somewhere to the left of the person drinking tea##5
 5. the person eating carrot is not to the left of the person traveling to marseilles##8
 6. the person traveling to london is somewhere to the right of the person drinking lemonade##5
 7. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the person eating kiwi##1
 8. the person drinking sprite is on the far left##1
 9. the gothic-revival house is somewhere to the left of the tower house##5
10. the gothic-revival house is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to miami##5
11. the person drinking tea is somewhere to the right of the gothic-revival house##5
12. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person eating carrot##1
13. the person traveling to nizza is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to marseilles##5
14. the craftsman house is the person drinking lemonade##1
15. the person eating cherry is on the left or right of the person traveling to marseilles##3
16. the gothic-revival house is not to the right of the person drinking tea##8
17. the gothic-revival house is the person traveling to london##1

