 4. the person driving the subway and the person eating cucumber have the same parity positions##9
 5. the fan punk is somewhere to the left of the person driving the motorbike##5
 6. the person eating apricot is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in november##5
 7. the person eating lime is on the far right##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the fan gospel##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in april and the person eating apricot have the same parity positions##9
10. the person driving the motorbike is the person eating cucumber##1
11. the fan gospel is not to the left of the fan punk##8
12. the person eating cucumber is not to the left of the fan salsa##8
13. the person driving the train is on the right of the person eating garlic##1
14. the person eating apricot and the fan salsa have the same parity positions##9
15. the person who's birthday is in february is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in november and the person eating cucumber##7

